  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2099164/" class="title-link">其实被逼着也没什么不好</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2099164"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ChloeW/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3593782-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ChloeW/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">某</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-28"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-28 03:50:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2099164_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  基本上看这书的时光，就集中在高二高三的语文早读。  高二时，老师是力荐还是逼着全班要买，已经不记得了。总之要是只是自己在书店碰着，是绝对不会下手买的。那时的自己，一来没兴趣，二来没功底。大雅之物，心生畏惧。  理科班，每星期的六个早上会被分割成3天语文，3天英语...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2099164/#comments">(42回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">127有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
