  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3508482">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3508482/" class="title-link">这个版本伴我10年之久</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3508482"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/44391303/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44391303-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/44391303/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">宋诗诗</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-05 20:28:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3508482_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是我父亲的书，一直压在他的书箱底，直到10年前某个中午，搬出来晒，我把它拾起，这一拾跟随我到了今天，我记得以前暑假黄昏时候，我便会在灯下读，一直读到心中清凉，夜寂静的能拧出水来。嗨，感觉很好，于是一发不可收拾的喜欢唐诗喜欢宋词，喜欢诗歌。。。。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
